title: I LOVE LISTS
description: I LOVE LISTS No one wants this, Instagram. How to ripen bananas faster. David Lynch’s enduring impact on photography. The difference between good & bad cholesterol. How will California’s fires affect wildlife? Hello, dream home. Trees become ART! Discoball: snail/plant/globe Time travel to homes in the 1950s. Imagine how gassy this taste test was. What a cute kitchenette! Inside the studio of a costume designer. WOW. A look at home design that shouldn’t exist. Groceries you need for a natural disaster. Speaking of: TJ’s pantry staples + pantry meals I am team Do-Si-Do & Tagalong (GS cookies) Pizza Cinnamon Toast Crunch? How about NO? Let’s learn about the names of Full Moons! Weekend baking: Sweet Potato Cornbread My word of the year is… Hi friends! I’m excited to announce that I’ll be hosting a monthly Zoom meetup Show & Tell for the Currently Workbook this year! Our first hangout is happening next Friday, January 31, from 5–6 PM PST. I’ll help you keep track of time by showing you how I do it! Have a great weekend. xo- Tracy The post I LOVE LISTS appeared first on Shutterbean.
excerpt: Welcome to I LOVE LISTS. It's Friday and Tracy of Shutterbean.com shares her finds from the internet on a weekly list called I LOVE LISTS!
